data.description: Centrally located, well maintained, 2 bedroom, 1 bath bungalow with 2 car detached garage. Vinyl siding and windows, rear covered patio, covered front porch. Very low maintenance property.  Front and rear parking features. Roof is approximately 6 years old. Call and agent today before this gem is gone!
